      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SKETCH (4) resumes here, boasting strong formlines last time in work. She got over a bit more ground but fancy 1200m is right in her wheelhouse. Fifth in a Listed race two back reads very well for this and if she's sharp enough she'll go close. CATWALK ICON (2) resumed with a smart maiden win at Ballarat as a short-priced favourite, leading throughout to score by two lengths. She can only improve off that and maps for every hope on speed again. PERSIAN CAVIAR (1) ran quite well fresh in a BM70 at Sandown Lakeside when getting home late. Up in the weights now given she's back to a BM62 but she's still got plenty of upside and can figure. ECO FORCE (3) is struggling to find another win but continues to race well and has strong each-way claims once more. SERINDA (5) is in the mix.",
